ktens forlag  p isbn  solagurenbeascoa de corral félix jacobsen objects and furniture design  barcelona ed poligrafa  pages isbn    solagurenbeascoa de corral félix arne jacobsen edificios públicos public buildings  barcelona ed gustavo gili  pages isbn  solagurenbeascoa de corral félix arne jacobsen approach to his complete works  link to ed arkitektens forlag  copenhague ed arkitektens forlag  pages isbn  solagurenbeascoa de corral félix arne jacobsen approach to his complete works  link to ed arkitektens forlag  copenhague ed arkitektens forlag  pages isbn  solagurenbeascoa de corral félix arne jacobsen drawings   copenhague ed arkitektens forlag  pages isbn  solagurenbeascoa de corral félix arne jacobsen  pekin ed china national publications  pages isbn  external linksedit wikimedia commons has media related to arne jacobsen arne jacobsen at the archinform database arne jacobsen portrait and photos of his most important furniture designs reflections on a soup spoon by alice rawsthorn international herald tribune may   authority control worldcat identities viaf  lccn n isni     gnd  selibr  sudoc  bnf cb data bibsys  ulan  ndl  kulturnav id rkd  retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlearnejacobsenoldid categories danish textile designers births deathsroyal danish academy of fine arts alumniarne jacobsendanish architectsdanish designersdanish furniture designersfunctionalist architectsmodernist architectsmodernist designersmodernist architecture in scandinaviaarchitects from copenhagendesigners from copenhagendanish jewshonorary fellows of the american institute of architectsjewish architectsarne jacobsen buildingsrecipients of the eckersberg medalrecipients of the cf hansen medalthcentury american architectsrecipients of the prince eugen medalhidden categories articles with hcardswikipedia articles with viaf identifierswikipedia articles with lccn identifierswikipedia articles with isni identifierswikipedia articles with gnd identifierswikipedia articles 